headline: The Coca-Cola Company Announces Timing of Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Earnings Release
summary: ATLANTA, January 13, 2026--The Coca-Cola Company today announced it will release fourth quarter and full year 2025 financial results Feb. 10 before the New York Stock Exchange opens. The release will be followed by an investor conference call at 8:30 a.m. ET to discuss the results.
